  "description": "In the quantum realm of the subatomic library, where particles and probabilities entangle to write the universe's grand narrative, a photon named Quilla blinked out of existence. The usual suspects in this probabilistic whodunit were nowhere and everywhere at once—entangled in a superposition of states.",
